/>\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">曹婦與狗不得內進（狗？就係講緊你啊油飯）</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJykxHC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJykxHC.png&h=492037c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>入黎討論前 請先睇曹柔里嘅罪</strong></span></span><br />\n注：如果唔想受到極大驚嚇建議唔好開自動LOAD圖，你可以選擇逐張㩒以一個循序漸進嘅方式去提高自己嘅接受能力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zzpEH7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zzpEH7.gif&h=313c0912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nY04WKG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnY04WKG.gif&h=5df81725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感謝塔諾巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">老鼠屎曹柔里</span></strong><br />\nIdol School 時期：<br />\n一、出曬名靠扮有情上位<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/09/03/LH0K2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2FLH0K2f.png&h=0453d0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二、評價舞台環節  見到有組員0票 大家都被隊友既零分嚇到的時候 佢自己微微的笑左一下 咁岩就比鏡頭影到 反應如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/183734_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F183734_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=b8bbc6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三、偶校開學之後都無沖涼 好唔注重衛生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyfetVc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyfetVc.png&h=6d87c7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPD48 時期：<br />\n四、個人評價唱唱下停係度 仲好淡定 PD史上第一次有人由A跌到F 當然會多啲鏡頭<br />\n五、參加日韓合作節目 開頭仲扮到好nice咁話會幫朱里 但練習時帶住<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>慰安婦徽章</strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/000624_79924e6172164ef70f197aa7ff5ab0ee.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F000624_79924e6172164ef70f197aa7ff5ab0ee.gif&h=80521caf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/000632_7e53c70ccb91bbf76093704c1d393aec.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F000632_7e53c70ccb91bbf76093704c1d393aec.gif&h=ddc9a402&s={SIZE}\" /> (詳：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/youNoV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/youNoV</a>) 完全唔尊重日本妹 前期節目花絮都無見過佢同日本妹交流 就後期淨係識痴住話題性高既nako<br />\n六、Position評價明明唱得無羅高恩好 都要爭Main Vocal 最後要成組降key就佢 仲要羅高恩教返佢點唱<br />\n七、第二次排名公佈 喊到要喊出聲先有人知佢喊緊 但一滴眼淚都無 虛偽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/210754_24793cdc7720db9b1be5d22d83b1fe86.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F210754_24793cdc7720db9b1be5d22d83b1fe86.gif&h=53022010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n八、Concept評價開頭話想換歌 但之後踢人走又跪哂地話想留低唔唱main vocal都得 留低之後又搶過<br />\n九、Concept評價傾踢邊個走期間無啦啦唱1000% 同公司狗竹都忍唔住串佢話歌詞都背好 暗指某婦係咪準備好過去<br />\n某婦努力練習無白費到，終於係出道showcon唱到一直好想唱嘅1000%<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/23/galR2K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2FgalR2K.png&h=b651ea12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十、mnet製造天使鏡頭 前面係嘈婦入去試唱完To touch you高音 雖然大家都聽得出佢上唔到F# 但ajy莫名其妙剪咗句對錄音室講F#唱到了 但嘈婦明明係佢哋身後 唔通有兩個油b？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAJG2Bs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAJG2Bs.jpg&h=89348b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下係某婦同AJY嘅完美配合<br />\n十一、Final揀位 瘋狂比人踢走 大大聲講無野話唔緊要 下一個shot即刻播海允比人踢完喊 成功營造天使image<br />\n十二、Final首歌降key唱 soyou仲要讚佢 明明降key其他人都唱到 AJY捧佢捧到出哂面<br />\n十三、最後排名公佈 上次18名升到第3名 扮驚訝 扮感動 但一滴眼淚都無 睇下同樣情況既安有真 金珉周同金彩元 反